-- Kandarian’s Pay at MetLife More Than Doubles to $10.6 Million
-- B y   A n d r e w   F r y e
-- 2012-03-26T20:20:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-26/kandarian-s-pay-at-metlife-more-than-doubles-to-10-6-million.html
Steven Kandarian ’s compensation at
 MetLife Inc. (MET)  more than doubled last year as he was promoted to
chief executive officer of the largest U.S. life insurer.  Kandarian was awarded $10.6 million for last year,
including a $3 million bonus, compared with about $4.2 million
in 2010 when he was chief investment officer, the New York-based
company said today in a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
